data.description: Welcome to this stunning property with a natural color palette throughout, creating a calming atmosphere. The kitchen boasts a nice backsplash, adding a touch of elegance. The abundance of other rooms provides flexible living space, perfect for customization. The primary bathroom features a separate tub and shower, offering relaxation and convenience. Additionally, it includes double sinks for added functionality and good under sink storage for organization. Outside, the fenced-in backyard ensures privacy and security, while the sitting area is ideal for enjoying outdoor gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Visit now and envision the possibilities! This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
